### AWS Bedrock Cost Tracking - Nova Pro
# Automatic cost tracking for AWS Bedrock requests
# Note: AWS Bedrock requires AWS SDK authentication (cannot use pure HTTP)
# This example shows the request format. Use the NPM package for actual implementation.

POST https://bedrock-runtime.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/model/amazon.nova-pro-v1:0/invoke
Content-Type: application/json
CostKatana-Auth: Bearer YOUR_COSTKATANA_KEY
CostKatana-Project-Id: YOUR_PROJECT_ID
CostKatana-Property-Provider: aws-bedrock
CostKatana-Property-Model-Family: nova

{
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Explain the benefits of serverless architecture."
    }
  ],
  "inferenceConfig": {
    "maxTokens": 1000,
    "temperature": 0.7
  }
}

